ide investors: =E2=80=9CPart of a sell-side analyst's job is to articulate =
different flavors of the current buy-side consensus. =E2=80=A6 So buy-side =
analysts talk to sell-side analysts partly because other buy-side analysts =
do; research quality ends up being a Schelling Point for arranging even hig=
her-quality discussions with opinionated, well-informed people on either si=
