the spread between buyers and sellers is too high and there's no liquidity.=
 The function of sell-side analysts is to smooth the flow of information, t=
o articulate what the relevant views are, and to connect people, directly o=
r indirectly, with other people who will change their minds.=E2=80=9D</p>
